                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18121202-115-off669 t18121202-115-crimeloc672"></join>. On the 25th of November, about half after five in the evening, I saw the prisoner in the act of breaking the pipe off. After he had broken it off I let him go to the distance of you to me. I went and took it on his person, then I took him to Lambeth-street office. This is the pipe; it was affixed to a wall leading to the house.</p>
